courier-imap: courier-imap (IMAP server that uses Maildirs)
courier-imap:
courier-imap: Courier-IMAP is a fast, scalable, enterprise IMAP server that uses
courier-imap: Maildirs. With the built-in IMAP and POP3 aggregation proxy in
courier-imap: Courier-IMAP 4.0, the only practical limit to Courier's horizontal
courier-imap: scalability is available LAN bandwidth. Please note that this IMAP
courier-imap: server does NOT handle traditional mailbox files (/var/spool/mail,
courier-imap: and derivatives), it was written and optimized for the specific
courier-imap: purpose of providing IMAP access to Maildirs.
courier-imap: http://www.courier-mta.org/imap/
courier-imap: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
